OL,3,CGermans are buying less beer due to
OL,4,Chealth concerns
OL,6,FGerman beer sales were down 4.5% in
OL,7,F2023 compared to the previous year,
OL,8,Fresuming a long-term trend of the
OL,9,Fnation famous for Oktoberfest drinking
OL,10,Fless.
OL,12,FGerman-based breweries and
OL,13,Fdistributors sold about 8.4 billion
OL,14,Flitres of beer last year, the Federal
OL,15,FStatistical Office said, while
OL,16,FGermans, who make up more than 80% of
OL,17,Fthe sales of German beer, bought 4.2%
OL,18,Fless beer than in 2022.
