OL,3,CGermans are buying less beer due to
OL,4,Chealth concerns
OL,6,FThat figure doesn't include non-
OL,7,Falcoholic beer and beer imported from
OL,8,Foutside the European Union.
OL,10,FGerman beer sales bucked the trend in
OL,11,F2022 with a 2.7% uptick in sales after
OL,12,Fdemand rose following the end of Covid-
OL,13,F19 restrictions, but in 2023 sales
OL,14,Fwere back on the decline.
OL,16,FGerman brewers have been struggling
OL,17,Fwith a long-term downward trend
OL,18,Ffuelled by health concerns and other
OL,19,Ffactors.
