OL,6,FThe statistics office said last year's
OL,7,Fsales were 11.3% lower than in 2013
OL,8,Fand 25.3% lower than in 1993.
OL,10,FEurope has the highest proportion of
OL,11,Falcohol drinkers in the world,
OL,12,Faccording to the World Health
OL,13,FOrganization, with seven of the 10
OL,14,Fcountries with the highest per-capita
OL,15,Flevels of alcohol consumptions in the
OL,16,Fregion.
