OL,3,CGermans are buying less beer due to
OL,4,Chealth concerns
OL,6,FBut like many European countries,
OL,7,FGermany has seen alcohol consumptions
OL,8,Fdrop and non-alcoholic beverages boom
OL,9,Fas people become more wary of the
OL,10,Fhealth effects of alcohol.
OL,12,FThe amount of low- and no-alcohol
OL,13,Fdrinks sold in the EU increased in
OL,14,Fvolume from 0.59 billion litres to
OL,15,F1.38 billion litres between 2013 and
OL,16,F2019, according to 2022 research
OL,17,Fcarried out at Maastricht University
OL,18,Fin The Netherlands.
